Class GObjectTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • adventure2D.project.GObjectTest

  • public class GObjectTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This test class does test the GObject class by using the GameObject class (because GObject is abstract). It actually only test the most simple getters so it isn't actually at all useful.
